==English==

===Interjection===
'''[[let's|let’s]] [[go]]!'''

# [[First-person]] plural [[imperative]] of '''to [[go]]'''.
#: '''''Let’s go''' to the beach next Saturday.''
# [[hurry up|Hurry up]], be quick.

====Synonyms====
*{{italbrac-colon|hurry up}} be [[quick]], [[chop chop]], [[come on]], [[get a move on]], [[hurry up]], [[look lively]], [[shake a leg]]

